Description: From the publisher: "The campus culture festival is coming up for the students of Class 2-A." That means starting an all-girl band, despite the keyboardist being a boy.
Title: NEON GENESIS: EVANGELION, VOL. 10
Author: Osamu Takahashi

Description: Princess Mina has set up a haven, off the coast of Japan, for her vampire people, but danger lurks in the form of Lord Ivanovic who wants Mina as his vampire bride.
Title: DANCE IN THE VAMPIRE BUND, VOL. 11
Author: Nozomu Tamaki

Description: Naruto, who wants to be a great ninja, is locked in a battle to decide the fate of the land.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 54
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO+VAMPIRE SEASON II, VOL. 7
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: The teenage detective Jimmy Kudo is trapped in the body of a child. While he searches for a cure, he solves tough cases like the one in this volume: worth 10 million yen!
Title: CASE CLOSED, VOL. 41
Author: Gosho Aoyama

Description: Fame, romance and broken hearts. In this installment, the girls learn about the power of love.
Title: SKIP BEAT!, VOL. 26
Author: Yoshiki Nakamura

Description: After the death of her brother, Teru has been receiving comforting messages from Daisy, who communicates through her brother’s cell phone. In this installment, Teru learns more about her brother’s past.
Title: DENGEKI DAISY, VOL. 8
Author: Kyousuke Motomi

Description: Naruto, who wants to be a great ninja, must confront his inner demons at the Waterfall of Truth.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 53
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Welcome to the world of the high-flying arms dealer Koko Hekmatyar and her band of mercenaries.
Title: JORMUNGAND, VOL. 8
Author: Keitaro Takahashi

Description: Isn’t being a kid hard enough? For this group, who are also part bird, nothing comes easy.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE MANGA, VOL. 5
Author: James Patterson
